<!-- Main Content -->
<main class="main">
<div class="container">

<!-- Overview Section -->
<section id="overview" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">📋</div><h3>Executive Overview</h3><span class="tag">RFC-FORGE-A2UI-001</span></div>
<p>The <strong>Flint A2UI Component Registry</strong> is a domain-agnostic, metadata-driven system that enables AI agents to discover, select, compose, and render user interface components through structured JSON references.</p>
<h4>Core Philosophy</h4>
<p>Agents do not generate raw HTML/CSS. They reference <strong>constrained component identifiers</strong> with structured parameters, and the registry handles the rendering, data binding, and lifecycle management.</p>
<ul style="margin:12px 0 12px 24px;color:var(--txtm);">
<li><strong>Security</strong> — No arbitrary markup injection</li>
<li><strong>Consistency</strong> — All UIs follow the same design system</li>
<li><strong>Composability</strong> — Components nest and combine predictably</li>
<li><strong>Accessibility</strong> — Base primitives include ARIA roles</li>
<li><strong>Performance</strong> — Pre-optimized rendering paths</li>
</ul>
</section>

<!-- Component Primitives Section -->
<section id="primitives" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">🧩</div><h3>Base Component Primitives</h3><span class="tag">30+ Components</span></div>
<p>All A2UI components are classified into six taxonomic categories. Each primitive has a canonical JSON schema, HTMX rendering, and semantic embedding for agent discovery.</p>

<h4 id="layout">Layout Primitives</h4>
<div class="comp-grid">
<div class="comp-item">
<h4>📦 Stack / Container</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;">
<div style="padding:12px;background:var(--s3);border:1px solid var(--s4);border-radius:6px;"><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--txtd);">Stack Item 1</span></div>
<div style="padding:12px;background:var(--s3);border:1px solid var(--s4);border-radius:6px;"><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--txtd);">Stack Item 2</span></div>
<div style="padding:12px;background:var(--s3);border:1px solid var(--s4);border-radius:6px;"><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--txtd);">Stack Item 3</span></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"stack","direction":"vertical","gap":"8px","items":["Item 1","Item 2","Item 3"]}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>⊞ Grid</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;">
<div style="padding:16px;background:var(--s3);border:1px solid var(--s4);border-radius:6px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:12px;">A</span></div>
<div style="padding:16px;background:var(--s3);border:1px solid var(--s4);border-radius:6px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:12px;">B</span></div>
<div style="padding:16px;background:var(--s3);border:1px solid var(--s4);border-radius:6px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:12px;">C</span></div>
<div style="padding:16px;background:var(--s3);border:1px solid var(--s4);border-radius:6px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:12px;">D</span></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"grid","columns":2,"gap":"8px","items":["A","B","C","D"]}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>◫ Split Pane</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div style="display:flex;gap:1px;background:var(--s4);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;">
<div style="flex:1;padding:20px;background:var(--s3);text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:12px;">Left Pane</span></div>
<div style="flex:1;padding:20px;background:var(--s3);text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:12px;">Right Pane</span></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"split_pane","ratio":0.5,"orientation":"horizontal"}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>🃏 Panel / Card</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div class="card" style="margin:0;">
<div class="card-h">Card Title</div>
<div class="card-d">Card content with description text that wraps to multiple lines.</div>
<button class="btn btn-p btn-sm">Action</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"card","title":"Card Title","description":"...","action":{"label":"Action"}}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>📜 Scroll Area</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div style="max-height:80px;overflow-y:auto;background:var(--s3);border:1px solid var(--s4);border-radius:6px;padding:8px;">
<div style="padding:6px;font-size:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--s4);">Item 1</div>
<div style="padding:6px;font-size:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--s4);">Item 2</div>
<div style="padding:6px;font-size:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--s4);">Item 3</div>
<div style="padding:6px;font-size:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--s4);">Item 4</div>
<div style="padding:6px;font-size:12px;">Item 5</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"scroll_area","max_height":"200px","content":"..."}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>— Divider</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div style="padding:16px 0;">
<div style="font-size:12px;margin-bottom:8px;">Section A</div>
<div style="height:1px;background:var(--s4);margin:8px 0;"></div>
<div style="font-size:12px;margin-top:8px;">Section B</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"divider","style":"horizontal"}</div>
</div>
</div>

<h4 id="data-display">Data Display Primitives</h4>
<div class="comp-grid">
<div class="comp-item">
<h4>📊 Table</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<table class="tbl">
<thead><tr><th>Name</th><th>Role</th><th>Status</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>Alice</td><td>Admin</td><td><span class="bd-g">Active</span></td></tr>
<tr><td>Bob</td><td>Editor</td><td><span class="bd-y">Pending</span></td></tr>
<tr><td>Carol</td><td>Viewer</td><td><span class="bd-r">Inactive</span></td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"table","columns":["Name","Role","Status"],"rows":[["Alice","Admin","Active"],...]}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>☰ List</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div style="border:1px solid var(--s4);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;">
<div style="padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--s4);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><div class="av av-sm">A</div><span style="font-size:13px;">Alice Chen</span></div>
<div style="padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--s4);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><div class="av av-sm" style="color:var(--gr);">B</div><span style="font-size:13px;">Bob Smith</span></div>
<div style="padding:10px 14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><div class="av av-sm" style="color:var(--yl);">C</div><span style="font-size:13px;">Carol Wu</span></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"list","items":[{"avatar":"A","title":"Alice"},...]}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>🌳 Tree</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div style="font-size:13px;padding:8px;">
<div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;margin-bottom:4px;"><span>▼</span><strong>src</strong></div>
<div style="margin-left:20px;margin-bottom:4px;"><span style="color:var(--txtd);">├─ components</span></div>
<div style="margin-left:20px;margin-bottom:4px;"><span style="color:var(--txtd);">├─ pages</span></div>
<div style="margin-left:20px;"><span style="color:var(--txtd);">└─ utils</span></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"tree","nodes":[{"label":"src","children":[...]}]}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>🏷️ Badge</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
<span class="bd-g">Active</span><span class="bd-y">Pending</span><span class="bd-r">Error</span><span class="bd-e">Beta</span><span class="bd-c">New</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"badge","label":"Active","variant":"success"}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>👤 Avatar</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;">
<div class="av">JD</div><div class="av av-g">🏢</div><div class="av av-sm">A</div><div class="av av-lg">+</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"avatar","initials":"JD","size":"md","shape":"circle"}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>📶 Progress Bar</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div class="pf"><span class="pf-l">Upload</span><div class="pf-b"><div class="pb"><div class="pb-b" style="width:65%"></div></div></div><span class="pf-v">65%</span></div>
<div class="pf"><span class="pf-l">Sync</span><div class="pf-b pb-g"><div class="pb"><div class="pb-b" style="width:92%"></div></div></div><span class="pf-v">92%</span></div>
<div class="pf"><span class="pf-l">CPU</span><div class="pf-b pb-c"><div class="pb"><div class="pb-b" style="width:34%"></div></div></div><span class="pf-v">34%</span></div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"progress_bar","label":"Upload","value":65,"max":100}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>📈 Metric Card</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div class="grid grid-2" style="gap:8px;">
<div class="mc" style="padding:12px;"><div class="mc-v">12,847</div><div class="mc-l">Users</div><div class="mc-d up">↑ 12.5%</div></div>
<div class="mc" style="padding:12px;"><div class="mc-v">$84.2K</div><div class="mc-l">Revenue</div><div class="mc-d down">↓ 3.2%</div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"metric_card","value":"12,847","label":"Users","trend":"+12.5%"}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>⏱️ Timeline</h4>
<div class="demo"><div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div class="tl">
<div class="tl-i"><div class="tl-d"></div><div class="tl-c">Project Created</div><div class="tl-t">2024-01-15 09:00</div><div class="tl-x">Initial setup completed</div></div>
<div class="tl-i"><div class="tl-d"></div><div class="tl-c">First Deployment</div><div class="tl-t">2024-01-20 14:30</div><div class="tl-x">v0.1.0 released to staging</div></div>
<div class="tl-i"><div class="tl-d"></div><div class="tl-c">Production Launch</div><div class="tl-t">2024-02-01 10:00</div><div class="tl-x">Live on production</div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"timeline","events":[{"title":"...","timestamp":"...","description":"..."}]}</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</body></html>


<!-- Input Primitives -->
<h4 id="input">Input Primitives</h4>
<div class="comp-grid">

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>📝 Text Input</h4>
<div class="demo">
<div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div class="fg" x-data="{count:0}">
<label class="lbl">Username</label>
<input type="text" class="inp" placeholder="Enter username..." hx-validate="true" hx-post="/api/validate-username" hx-target="#uname-feedback" hx-trigger="keyup changed delay:500ms" hx-indicator="#uname-spinner" x-model="count" @input="count = $event.target.value.length">
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:4px;">
<span id="uname-spinner" class="htmx-indicator" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--cy);">Validating...</span>
<span id="uname-feedback" style="font-size:11px;"></span>
<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--txtd);" x-text="count + ' chars'"></span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"text_input","label":"Username","placeholder":"...","validation":"required|min:3","hx_validate":true,"hx_post":"/api/validate-username"}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>🔢 Number Input</h4>
<div class="demo">
<div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div class="fg">
<label class="lbl">Quantity</label>
<div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;">
<button class="btn btn-s btn-i" @click="$refs.qty.value = Math.max(0, parseInt($refs.qty.value||0)-1)">−</button>
<input type="number" class="inp" x-ref="qty" value="5" min="0" max="100" step="1" style="text-align:center;width:80px;">
<button class="btn btn-s btn-i" @click="$refs.qty.value = Math.min(100, parseInt($refs.qty.value||0)+1)">+</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="demo-code">{"type":"number_input","label":"Quantity","min":0,"max":100,"step":1,"value":5}</div>
</div>

<div class="comp-item">
<h4>▼ Select / Dropdown</h4>
<div class="demo">
<div class="demo-label">Visual</div>
<div class="fg">
<label class="lbl">Department</label>
<select class="sel" hx-get="/api/teams" hx-target="#team-select" hx-trigger="change">
<option value="">Choose department...</option>
<option value="eng">Engineering</option>
<option value="design">Design</option>
<option value="product">Product</option>
<option value="marketing">Marketing</option>
</select>
