<!-- Registry Schema Section -->
<section id="registry-schema" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">🗄️</div><h3>Registry Schema</h3><span class="tag">PostgreSQL + pgvector</span></div>
<p>The registry schema consists of six core tables stored in PostgreSQL, with pgvector embeddings for semantic component discovery.</p>

<h4>Core Tables</h4>
<table class="tbl" style="margin:16px 0;">
<thead><tr><th>Table</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Key Columns</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><code>components</code></td><td>Component definitions</td><td>id, name, category, json_schema, embedding, htmx_template</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>applications</code></td><td>App registrations</td><td>id, name, domain, config_json, embedding</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>design_systems</code></td><td>Theme tokens</td><td>id, name, tokens_json, css_variables</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>bindings</code></td><td>DB field mappings</td><td>id, component_id, table_name, column_name, transform</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>events</code></td><td>Event definitions</td><td>id, name, payload_schema, handlers</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>embeddings</code></td><td>Semantic vectors</td><td>id, entity_type, entity_id, embedding vector(1536)</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<h4>JSON Schema Example</h4>
<pre><code>{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "type": {"type": "string", "enum": ["button"]},
    "label": {"type": "string", "maxLength": 50},
    "variant": {"type": "string", "enum": ["primary","secondary","ghost"]},
    "size": {"type": "string", "enum": ["sm","md","lg"]},
    "action": {"type": "string"},
    "hx_post": {"type": "string", "format": "uri"},
    "hx_target": {"type": "string"},
    "hx_swap": {"type": "string", "enum": ["innerHTML","outerHTML","beforeend"]}
  },
  "required": ["type", "label"]
}</code></pre>
</section>

<!-- Bindings Section -->
<section id="bindings" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">🔗</div><h3>Database Bindings</h3><span class="tag">Auto-binding</span></div>
<p>Components can be automatically bound to PostgreSQL tables and columns. When a table is registered, the registry suggests matching components based on column types and constraints.</p>

<h4>Binding Configuration</h4>
<pre><code>{
  "table": "users",
  "column": "email",
  "component": "text_input",
  "transform": {
    "validation": "required|email",
    "placeholder": "user@example.com",
    "label": "Email Address"
  }
}</code></pre>

<h4>Auto-binding Trigger</h4>
<pre><code>CREATE TRIGGER auto_bind_component
AFTER INSERT ON information_schema.columns
FOR EACH ROW
EXECUTE FUNCTION suggest_component_binding();</code></pre>
</section>

<!-- Design Bridge Section -->
<section id="design-bridge" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">🎨</div><h3>Open Design Bridge</h3><span class="tag">ODSF Import/Export</span></div>
<p>The registry can import and export design system definitions in the Open Design System Format (ODSF), enabling interoperability with design tools like Figma and Sketch.</p>

<h4>Import Function</h4>
<pre><code>SELECT import_odsf('{
  "name": "Flint Dark",
  "tokens": {
    "color": {
      "background": "#0B0F14",
      "surface": "#131A22",
      "primary": "#FF6A3D",
      "accent": "#34CFE6"
    },
    "typography": {
      "heading": "Space Grotesk",
      "body": "Inter",
      "mono": "JetBrains Mono"
    }
  }
}'::jsonb);</code></pre>
</section>

<!-- API Section -->
<section id="api" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">📡</div><h3>REST API</h3><span class="tag">5 Endpoint Groups</span></div>

<h4>Endpoints</h4>
<table class="tbl" style="margin:16px 0;">
<thead><tr><th>Method</th><th>Path</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><span class="bd-g">GET</span></td><td><code>/api/v1/components</code></td><td>List all components with filtering</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="bd-g">GET</span></td><td><code>/api/v1/components/{id}</code></td><td>Get component by ID or name</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="bd-e">POST</span></td><td><code>/api/v1/components/search</code></td><td>Semantic search with natural language</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="bd-g">GET</span></td><td><code>/api/v1/applications/{id}/components</code></td><td>List components for an application</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="bd-e">POST</span></td><td><code>/api/v1/render</code></td><td>Render component to HTML/HTMX</td></tr>
<tr><td><span class="bd-e">POST</span></td><td><code>/api/v1/compose</code></td><td>Compose multiple components</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<h4>Semantic Search Example</h4>
<pre><code>POST /api/v1/components/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "a form to collect user feedback with ratings",
  "limit": 5,
  "threshold": 0.7
}</code></pre>
</section>

<!-- A2A Section -->
<section id="a2a" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">🤝</div><h3>A2A Tasks</h3><span class="tag">16 Standard Tasks</span></div>
<p>The registry exposes 16 standard A2A tasks that agents can invoke to discover, compose, and manage components.</p>

<table class="tbl" style="margin:16px 0;">
<thead><tr><th>Task</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><code>list_components</code></td><td>List all components with optional filters</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>search_components</code></td><td>Semantic search by natural language query</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>get_component</code></td><td>Get component schema and metadata</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>compose_ui</code></td><td>Compose a multi-component UI from a description</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>render_component</code></td><td>Render a component to HTML/HTMX</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>register_component</code></td><td>Register a new component</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>update_component</code></td><td>Update component metadata</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>delete_component</code></td><td>Soft-delete a component</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>list_applications</code></td><td>List registered applications</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>get_application</code></td><td>Get application metadata</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>bind_table</code></td><td>Auto-bind components to a table</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>get_bindings</code></td><td>Get bindings for a table</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>import_odsf</code></td><td>Import ODSF design system</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>export_odsf</code></td><td>Export design system to ODSF</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>validate_ui</code></td><td>Validate a UI composition</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>generate_embedding</code></td><td>Generate semantic embedding</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</section>

<!-- MCP Section -->
<section id="mcp" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">🔧</div><h3>MCP Tools</h3><span class="tag">7 Tools</span></div>
<p>The registry exposes 7 MCP (Model Context Protocol) tools for integration with agent frameworks.</p>

<table class="tbl" style="margin:16px 0;">
<thead><tr><th>Tool</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><code>search_components</code></td><td>Search components by query string</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>get_component_schema</code></td><td>Get JSON schema for a component</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>compose_ui</code></td><td>Compose UI from component references</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>render_htmx</code></td><td>Render component to HTMX HTML</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>validate_composition</code></td><td>Validate component nesting</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>list_design_systems</code></td><td>List available design systems</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>get_binding_suggestions</code></td><td>Get auto-binding suggestions for a table</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</section>

<!-- Events Section -->
<section id="events" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">⚡</div><h3>Event-Driven Assembly</h3><span class="tag">Realtime</span></div>
<p>The registry uses PostgreSQL LISTEN/NOTIFY for real-time event propagation, enabling live UI updates when components change.</p>

<h4>Event Types</h4>
<table class="tbl" style="margin:16px 0;">
<thead><tr><th>Event</th><th>Channel</th><th>Payload</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><code>component_registered</code></td><td><code>a2ui_components</code></td><td>{id, name, category}</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>component_updated</code></td><td><code>a2ui_components</code></td><td>{id, changes}</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>composition_requested</code></td><td><code>a2ui_compose</code></td><td>{request_id, description, agent_id}</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>binding_created</code></td><td><code>a2ui_bindings</code></td><td>{id, table, column, component}</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>design_system_imported</code></td><td><code>a2ui_design</code></td><td>{id, name, token_count}</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</section>

<!-- Security Section -->
<section id="security" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">🔒</div><h3>Security Model</h3><span class="tag">RLS + JWT</span></div>
<p>All registry tables use PostgreSQL Row Level Security (RLS) with JWT claims. The security model follows the principle of least privilege.</p>

<h4>RLS Policies</h4>
<pre><code>CREATE POLICY component_read_policy ON components
FOR SELECT USING (jwt_claims ->> 'role' IN ('admin', 'developer', 'agent'));

CREATE POLICY component_write_policy ON components
FOR INSERT WITH CHECK (jwt_claims ->> 'role' = 'admin');</code></pre>
</section>

<!-- Roadmap Section -->
<section id="roadmap" class="sec">
<div class="sec-h"><div class="icon">🗺️</div><h3>Implementation Roadmap</h3><span class="tag">8 Milestones</span></div>

<table class="tbl" style="margin:16px 0;">
<thead><tr><th>Milestone</th><th>Deliverable</th><th>Status</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>M1</td><td>Core schema + 30 base primitives</td><td><span class="bd-g">Planned</span></td></tr>
<tr><td>M2</td><td>HTMX rendering engine</td><td><span class="bd-g">Planned</span></td></tr>
<tr><td>M3</td><td>Semantic embeddings + search</td><td><span class="bd-g">Planned</span></td></tr>
<tr><td>M4</td><td>Auto-binding pipeline</td><td><span class="bd-g">Planned</span></td></tr>
<tr><td>M5</td><td>A2A task surface</td><td><span class="bd-g">Planned</span></td></tr>
<tr><td>M6</td><td>MCP tool surface</td><td><span class="bd-g">Planned</span></td></tr>
<tr><td>M7</td><td>Event-driven assembly</td><td><span class="bd-g">Planned</span></td></tr>
<tr><td>M8</td><td>Production hardening</td><td><span class="bd-g">Planned</span></td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</section>

</div></main></div>

</body></html>
